{"groups":[{"groupKey":"120363427141316994@g.us","name":"COZE GK 21stJul Sandra Ross 4A","platform":"WhatsApp","propertyCode":"GK","messageCount":3,"lastActive":1784517994105,"messages":[{"sender":"Sandy Rhee Ross","text":"Hello!  I wanted to confirm the airport pickup for tomorrow from ICN to our rental?","ts":1784516218860},{"sender":"COZE_Jin","text":"Hello! @176412208173203 \n\nYes, absolutely. We are all set for your airport pickup from ICN to your rental tomorrow. \n\nWe look forward to welcoming you!","ts":1784516486638},{"sender":"Sandy Rhee Ross","text":"Great!  Thank you so much!","ts":1784517994105}]},{"groupKey":"120363407384623871@g.us","name":"120363407384623871@g.us","platform":"WhatsApp","messageCount":4,"lastActive":1784517548199,"messages":[{"sender":"Yu Gil","text":"Good morning Coze teamрҹҳҠ\nQuick question, how do we dispose of cardboard materials?","ts":1784512274992},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Please place the cardboard materials next to the outdoor trash bins. Our team will take care of them. Thank you! рҹҳҠ","ts":1784512536910},{"sender":"Yu Gil","text":"Ok thank you рҹҳҠ","ts":1784512669730},{"sender":"COZE_CYRUS","text":"Hello рҹҳҠ @188584162275518 \n\nYour airport transportation for tomorrowвҖҷs 4:30 a.m. departure has been fully arranged, and the driver has already been assigned. The driver will also assist you with moving and loading your luggage into the vehicle.\n\nAs your departure is very early, we hope you can get some comfortable rest as early as possible this evening.\n\nPlease also note that the building is mostly residential, and the neighbors will still be sleeping at that time. We would greatly appreciate it if you could prepare and leave as quietly and carefully as possible. рҹҷҸ\n\nThank you so much for your understanding and kind cooperation.\n\nCyrus\nGuest Care Team of COZE Hospitality 3.0","ts":1784517548199}]},{"groupKey":"kakao:301321483004194","name":"kakao:301321483004194","platform":"KakaoTalk","messageCount":1